column5: Here comes another storm!! Looks huge!!   dsn
I hate winter!! I cannot wait for spring fishing......
Yeah I'm kinda looking forward to spring also.  dsn

Looks like Whopper is gonna get Whopped again!  Since y'all were kind enough to share your COLD Canadian air masses with us a few weeks ago... I figured what the hell! I'll share of of my nice Gulf of Mexico moisture with y'all!!!  I can't help it if y'all let it freeze and turn to snow... that's Your fault!!!  Y'all have fun in that snow now... ya heah?

Your right on the money Glen, we are getting a ice storm right now rain mixed with ice, getting reel nasty. I was out on the ice all afternoon and when I came home I told my wife no way is it going to rain tonight "it's just to dang cold" WRONG.  Whopper
Eee doggies, I reckon' it's murder on the car washes. Just when ya get her all prettied up, It's a salt bath all over again.
MMM snow equals accumulation equals plowing equals money....come on snow!!!!!!
